00:44:29,566 --> 00:44:43,433
What we get here, and now I will turn to Gilles Deleuze, towards whom I am critical but he is a genius, has ingenious insights, Deleuze said that his thinking tries to construct

378
00:44:43,733 --> 00:44:51,466
a quote from Deleuze, a perception of reality as it was before or after man, humanity.

